activities.name: Get _File_List
activities.description: File List from Azure Blob storage

source.name: End Data of Latest Data Period

sqlReaderQuery.value:
SELECT  '@{pipeline().RunId}' AS RUN_ID
,'@{pipeline().DataFactory}' AS DATAFACTORY_NAME 
,'@{pipeline().Pipeline}' AS PIPELINE_NAME
,'@{item().name}' As file_name
,'Copy data 81 ' as Source
,'Azure Sql DB' as Destination
,'@{activity('Copy data 81').output.rowsRead}' as RowsRead
,'@{activity('Copy data 81').output.rowsCopied}' as RowsCopied
,'@{activity('Copy data 81').output.copyDuration}' as copyDuration
,'@{activity('Copy data 81').output.executionDetails[0].start}' as Execution_start
,'@{activity('Copy data 81').output.executionDetails[0].status}' as Execution_Status
,'1' as Execution_flag
,'@{utcnow()}' as ErrorLoggedTime

SELECT  '@{pipeline().RunId}' AS RUN_ID
,'@{pipeline().DataFactory}' AS DATAFACTORY_NAME 
,'@{pipeline().Pipeline}' AS PIPELINE_NAME
,'@{item().name}' As file_name
,'Copy data 81 ' as Source
,'Azure Sql DB' as Destination
,ISNULL('@{activity('Copy data 81').output.rowsRead}',0) as RowsRead
,ISNULL('@{activity('Copy data 81').output.rowsCopied}',0) as RowsCopied
,ISNULL('@{activity('Copy data 81').output.copyDuration}',0) as copyDuration
,'@{activity('Copy data 81').output.executionDetails[0].start}' as Execution_start
,'@{activity('Copy data 81').output.executionDetails[0].status}' as Execution_Status
,'2' as Execution_flag
,'@{utcnow()}' as ErrorLoggedTime
,'@{replace(activity('Copy data 81').output.errors[0].Message,'''','')}' as ErrorDescriprion
